        "created_at": "2018-11-25T15:26:14.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Great note, William!  I\u2019m one of the fans.  Just popped a 1996 last week.  Chambers got in the 1970 and 1982, I blinked, and they were gone.  A mistake as they source from the Chateau.</p>\n<p>Have you tried the new releases, 2010 and 2009?</p>",
