        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"147562\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Great note, William!  I\u2019m one of the fans.  Just popped a 1996 last week.  Chambers got in the 1970 and 1982, I blinked, and they were gone.  A mistake as they source from the Chateau.</p>\n<p>Have you tried the new releases, 2010 and 2009?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I own a few but haven\u2019t opened any. The youngest vintage I have actually drunk is the 2004!</p>",
